    "Discovering the best prompts involves picking specific tokens, which can be achieved through either manual exploration or non-gradient-based search techniques [40].The vector 𝒙 𝑝 is then encoded by transformer layers, resulting in a high-dimensional projection 𝒙 ℎ ∈ R 𝐻 𝐼 ×𝐷, where 𝐻 𝐼 is the number of image features in high dimensional space."
